name: Maple Sunspot
description:
The snowy branches of a maple tree are silhouetted by the warm light of the late day sun.

Photographed 2017. GIF Created 2021. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing and GIF building.

1024x685 GIF

Black and White Series: Gift for collectors of B/W series diptychs and 1/1s.
